titleStmt.title: Ölkofra þáttur according to AM 132 fol : A digital edition

publicationStmt.date: Converted from database and adapted to Menota, 26 October 2017

sourceDesc.bibl: Photographic facsimiles of ff. 147-149 from the Arnamagnæan Collection in Reykjavík.

msIdentifier.msName: Ölkofra þáttur according to AM 132 fol (Möðruvallabók)

msContents.p: OEH: Description of the contents of the manuscript may be added here

origin.p: This manuscript was written in Iceland c. 1330-1370.

projectDesc.p: This encoding follows the standard set out in The Menota handbook (version 3.0), at http://www.menota.org/handbook.xml.
The encoded text has numbered pagebreaks, columnbreaks and linebreaks according to the manuscript.

normalization.p: This manuscript text has been encoded on three levels: facsimile, diplomatic and normalised.

correction.p: OEH: Comments on the correction may be added here.

interpretation.p: Words missing in the manuscript text and added by the editor are neither lemmatized nor morphologically analyzed.

Verses and headings are only given in facsimile form and are neither analyzed nor lemmatized. This is due to the fact that the original project was restricted to the prose text written by the main scribe.

revisionDesc.change: 2021-07-11 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: Revised and updated the header

2021-05-06 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: changed the following character entities according to the latest version of the Menota entity list: drotisup > drotinodotsup, hisup > hinodotsup, kisup > kinodotsup, thornisup > thorninodotsup, btit > ber, drottit > droter, htit > her, ktit > ker, thorntit > thorner
2020-03-12 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: Made some changes of the msa annotation; eE to eP, and yAD to yDA
2017-11-14 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: Inserted "cb" elements in addition to "pb" elements
2017-11-02 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: Added a "msName" in order to make the text accessible in Corpuscle
2017-10-29 Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen: Corrected the encoding of the file in order to make it valid, and interpreted a number of character entities
2017-summer Andrea de Leeuw van Weenen: Distinguished between capitals/versals and enlarged minuscules
2017-summer Andrea de Leeuw van Weenen: Added code for linebreaks
